   Set a Alias will cause an error,if the dataset have a dynamic parameter involved

    1. new a sampledb datasource and dataset
    2. create a report parameter: "NewParameter", List Box, Dynamic.

    4. edit the dataset, go to the "Output Column" pane and set an Alias
